title: Mighty Animals
creator: Jennie Irene Mix
description: LibriVox recording of Mighty Animals, by Jennie Irene Mix. A book about dinosaurs written for children. In short, easy to read chapters designed to keep the interest of juvenile readers. (Summary by Guero) For further information, including links to online text, reader information, RSS feeds, CD cover or other formats (if available), please go to the LibriVox catalog page for this recording.
